songs.title: Love Runs Out (Disciples Remix)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I'll be your light, your match, your burning sun

[Hook]
'Til the love runs out
Out...
'Til the love runs out
Out...
'Til the love runs out
Out...
'Til the love runs out
'Til the love runs out
'Til the love runs out

[Verse 1]
I'll be your light, your match, your burning sun
I'll be your light, your match, your burning sun

[Hook]
'Til the love runs out
'Til the love runs out
Out...

[bridge]
For love, for hate
For gold, for rust
For diamonds, for dust

[Chorus]
'Til the love runs out

[Verse 1]
I'll be your light, your match, your burning sun
I'll be your light, your match, your burning sun
I'll be your light, your match, your burning sun

[Chorus]
'Til the love runs out
